{"tid":419761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地等一個人等到最心淡係發生咩事？","createTime":"2017-09-30T18:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T10:00:38.000Z","uid":133611,"like":73,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4c3141a91773b8db30c48f78dc13d08d987e82","tid":419761,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"係講physically 嘅等<br />\n<br />\n記得有一年個情人節<br />\n我Ex　當時話會接我落堂然後去食飯<br />\n我落堂之後打電話比佢<br />\n完全無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打比佢幾個鍾都完全無人聽，之後熄埋電話..<br />\n我就係間starbucks 等咗佢三個鍾，8pm等到11pm<br />\n<br />\n之後我見到佢前女友post　咗IG　同佢嘅合照<br />\n雖然無佢個樣　但我認得佢件衫　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有自己死死氣番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後佢凌晨先打比我話Sorry屋企人有嘢要佢幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e38f9c1ddf1926b947426e6df35c08a559cced9","tid":419761,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75d0737ad096a86fd0c04c4dc8beedd8190c333","tid":419761,"uid":133611,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:03:40.000Z","msg":"之後佢話　佢屋企人仲好衰　自己搭車走咗先<br />\n掉低佢一個人係XX番屋企（某地區）<br />\n但佢又唔記得　佢話過我知佢之前女朋友就係住XX<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係你講大話唔緊要<br />\n你真係以為我會信先好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f39aad1bdca32591f0cd7571c00f56d5ab2cf3f","tid":419761,"uid":59282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:07:50.000Z","msg":"最後點?"},{"pid":"42e2733caeabc03f52fc291c90874c29e6f12cac","tid":419761,"uid":133611,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後點?</blockquote><br />\n你指段感情？<br />\n佢最後