c=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我話唔好話咩你好鍾意我<br />\n根本做出嚟都唔係呢回事<br />\n到到你有一日遇到你真係愛嘅人你就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明咩叫珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係拒絕咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抱抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都一直覺得 當你真係遇到一個自己深愛嘅人<br />\n你會知道要點樣愛錫佢<br />\n唔會想佢傷心<br />\n愛係本能 唔需要學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a8d63ce6cc22d52d4339b10eb114853f20726b","tid":419761,"uid":21633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:29:50.000Z","msg":"話分開一陣睇下暑假見翻會唔會好d<br />\n點知等到原來自己一直帽緊都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed0e6401cacae049fbc9b7f2e47773d1a9c14b3","tid":419761,"uid":128720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:43:37.000Z","msg":"係第二度讀書 佢返咗去自己國家 但我無返香港<br />\n成個暑假都有一直Whatsapp佢 同埋一直都等佢返嚟<br />\n但佢都無乜點覆 到佢返嚟前一日佢同我講sorry 改咗機票無話你知<br />\n即刻心都淡埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後我頂唔順飛咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5a62f80da68e50a0421ec98a6514ac1b06591a","tid":419761,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係第二度讀書 佢返咗去自己國家 但我無返香港<br />\n成個暑假都有一直Whatsapp佢 同埋一直都等佢返嚟<br />\n但佢都無乜點覆 到佢返嚟前一日佢同我講sorry 改咗機票無話你知<br />\n即刻心都淡埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後我頂唔順飛咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLong D　真係上機一刻就會覺得打定輸數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}